Please read this entire file.

The "Visitor" bitmap fonts were created by Brian Kent (kentpw@norwich.net, http://www.aenigmafonts.com/) and came with the following disclaimer:

[start disclaimer]

-The font(s) in this zip file were created by me (Brian Kent).  All of my Fonts are Freeware, you can use them any way you want to (Personal use, Commercial use, or whatever).

-If you have a Font related site and would like to offer my fonts on your site, go right ahead. All I ask is that you keep this text file intact with the Font.

-You may not Sell or Distribute my Fonts for profit or alter them in any way without asking me first.  [e-mail -  kentpw@norwich.net]

[end disclaimer]

Permission was obtained for the fonts to be distributed freely with Epiar via e-mail on Monday, February 2, 2009. The e-mail is copied below:

